  • Package uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.memory

    • Class uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.memory.Generic_MemoryManager extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • HOOME

          boolean HOOME
          For storing the default as to whether OutOfMemoryErrors are handled.

        • HOOMEF

          boolean HOOMEF
          For use when OutOfMemory handling is definitely not wanted. It is thought better to have this rather than use a false value as and when as it allows for finding those parts of the code that are actually used in this regard.

        • HOOMET

          boolean HOOMET
          For use when OutOfMemory handling is definitely wanted. It is thought better to have this rather than use a false value as and when as it allows for finding those parts of the code that are actually used in this regard.

        • Memory_Threshold

          long Memory_Threshold
          Stores the amount of memory that is reserved and cleared for handling OutOfMemoryErrors should they be encountered.
